Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:47.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:52.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,お お...美味しい...かな...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:52.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,奥...奥利给...
Comment: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:52.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,好...好吃...大概吧...
